lenders.loan_because: StarFactree Foundation, Inc. supports the arts and education to promote unity and diversity through community based creative innovation and initiatives.
lenders.occupational_info: Just for Kids Las Vegas  is a series of summer workshops for young people in multiple locations, teaching them to connect and work together, in person and remotely, with audio/visual and Internet technologies. Teens in each city are taught teamwork skills, as well as social and technological skills in performances and audio/visual workshops facilitated by technologists and theater artists. They subsequently create a performance that occurs both live in theaters and online simultaneously.Starfactree Foundation facilitates supervised collaboration, learning and creating. In the pilot program, we will be working with young people  ages 13-16.  In a series of progressive workshops, they will learn technical skills such as video/audio production, networked  collaboration, digital storytelling, and streaming Internet media, while also developing social skills, creativity and communication skills through group work in improvisational theater, music and dance.
